583
00:45:23,100 --> 00:45:27,620
[Every lonely journey
ends in a fated encounter.]

584
00:45:27,700 --> 00:45:34,940
[Thank you for choosing When Destiny
Brings The Demon among countless options.]

585
00:45:36,100 --> 00:45:39,260
