Thank you, Boss.

593
00:45:58,470 --> 00:45:59,470
Grandmaster.

594
00:46:00,470 --> 00:46:01,470
Grandmaster!

595
00:46:03,590 --> 00:46:06,170
Because I hold you dear

596
00:46:07,550 --> 00:46:09,340
